                        <a href="/ask/qa22888/answer46493/" target="_blank">2013-03-28 17:40</a>
                        <a href="javascript:;" data-selector="showComment" data-type=""><em class="icons16 icons16-comment"></em>0条评论</a>
                    		<a href="javascript:;" class="report-answer" data-selector="report-answer">举报</a>
                    		<div data-selector="tpl-tips" class="tpl-tips"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="topic-review-box-block">
                    </div>
                </div>
            
                <div class="each-answer" data-repid="46485" data-authorid="029e3632b277e94d67c78c47907bb405" data-userkind="2">
                    <div class="clearfix top-bar">
                    	<!-- <dl> 人脉层  begin -->
	                    <dl class="asker-info">
	                        <dt>
	                            <img class="tinyFace" src="https://image0.lietou-static.com/normal/56e6135945ce672d5e8e8eb905a.jpg">
	                        </dt>
	                        <dd class="other-answer">
	                            <p class="other-answer-info">
	                            <span>常巧玲</span>
	                            
	                            
	                            </p>
	                            <p class="job-title">资深顾问(SC)</p>
	                        </dd>
	                    </dl>
	                    <!-- <dl> 人脉层 end  -->
	                    <!-- zan logo -->
	                    
	                    <a class="prime" data-param="qa_id=46485&amp;authorid=029e3632b277e94d67c78c47907bb405&amp;questionId=22888" data-selector="prime" href="javascript:;"><em class="icons16 icons16-prime"></em>1</a>
	                    
                     </div>
                    <p class="other-answer-point">
                    
                    按照工作年限补偿，工作满一年支付相当于一个月工资的经济补偿金，不足6个月支付半个月，超过6个月不足一年按一年计算，这里说的月工资按解除劳动关系前12个月劳动者的平均工资为基数，若平均工资高于当地社平工资3倍,只以社平工资3倍为基数。</p>
